title: That Metal Show S11E02 Bobby Blotzer, L.A. Guns.mkv
description: Bobby Blotzer sits down with hosts Eddie Trunk, Jim Florentine and Don Jamieson to discuss the past, present, and future of Ratt, as well as face the wrath of The Vault. Stephen Riley and Phil Lewis of L.A. Guns then join in on the conversation and address the warring factions of the two incarnations of their band. Don't miss the rock liquor nightcap as everyone gathers around the TMS bar for vodka, wine, and Bobby Blotzer's cheese. Steve Stevens shreds on guitar as this week's guest musician.
